<div class="inner cover">

  <h1>Whose Fans Are the Best?</h1>
  <p class="lead">Your favorite team lays it all on the line for YOU!</p>

  <p>Now itâ€™s your turn to compete. </p>

  <p>Ultimate Fan Base is going to be the place for fans to connect and compete. We're spreading the word now, and we're kicking off by giving you a chance to win some sweet swag by being the best fan base in the land. Here's all you have to do:</p>

  <p>Tell us who's your team. </p>

  <p>That's it.</p>

  <p>Every single fan of the team that gets the most love gets a free team sticker!</p>
  <%= form_for @user do |u| %>
    <div>
     <%= u.label :email %>
     <%= u.email_field :email %>
    </div>
    <div>
      <%= label_tag :conference %>
      <%= select_tag :conference, options_from_collection_for_select(Conference.all, :id, :name) %>
    </div>
    <div>
      <%= u.label :team_id, 'Team' %>
      <%= u.select :team_id, options_from_collection_for_select(Team.all, :id, :name) %>
    </div>
    <p class="lead">
      <%= u.submit 'Support Your Team Now!', class: 'btn btn-lg btn-default' %>
    </p>
  <% end %>
</div>
